              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Pairs of passivated, ion-implanted planar silicon",
                "detectors had a depletion depth of 100 microns and an",
                "active surface area of 100 mm2.",
                "Six pairs of detectors were used to measure the",
                "kinetic energies of the fission fragments and",
                "alpha particles."
              ]
            }
          ],
